org.ietf.nea.pb.batch

Class PbBatchHeaderBuilderIetf

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ietf.nea.pb.batch.PbBatchHeaderBuilderIetf
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TnccsBatchHeaderBuilder, TransmissionObjectBuilder<TnccsBatchHeader>, PbBatchHeaderBuilder

    public class PbBatchHeaderBuilderIetf
extends Object
implements PbBatchHeaderBuilder
    Builder to build a TNCCS batch header compliant to RFC 5793. It evaluates the given values and can be used in a fluent way.
